			<div class="featured-img-container">
			<img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.46.12-PM-1-726x400.png" title="Adam Morgan, John Berryman, Tilar J. Mazzeo, and more: 11 new books out today!">
								</div>
		<div class="story-heads">
		<h1>Adam Morgan, John Berryman, Tilar J. Mazzeo, and more: 11 new books out today!</h1>
			</div>
	</div>
										<div class="byline-date">
					<span class="byline"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/juliahass/"  title="Julia Hass">Julia Hass</a></span>
					<span class="hr"></span>
					<span class="date">December 9, 2025</span>
				</div>
						<div class="story-body">
								<p>Cozy winter season is upon us, and the publishing world is finally letting us catch up to their endless output. It&#8217;s time to peruse the &#8220;Best of&#8221; lists (like ours, <a href="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-43-favorite-books-of-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>) and discover all the great books we’ve missed. And yet, still, there is more out today: a biography of Margaret C. Anderson, a collection of unpublished John Berryman poems, this years collection of Best Debut Stories, and others that are sure to please. Happy reading, as always.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">*</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="255923" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2025-part-two/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr.jpg" data-orig-size="1400,2113" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Adam Morgan, A Danger to the Minds of Young Girls" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-199x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-678x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-255923" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-199x300.jpg" alt="Adam Morgan, A Danger to the Minds of Young Girls" width="199" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-199x300.jpg 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-678x1024.jpg 678w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-768x1159.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-1018x1536.jpg 1018w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-1357x2048.jpg 1357w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-danger-to-the-minds-of-young-girls-9781668053645_hr.jpg 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 199px) 100vw, 199px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Adam Morgan, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781668053645" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>A Danger to the Minds of Young Girls: Margaret C. Anderson, Book Bans, and the Fight to Modernize Literature</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Atria)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Adam Morgan’s wise and generous biography is wholly transportive and spellbinding. I was beguiled.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>Ling Ma</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263444" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/crony-henry-daddy-henry-lady-henry-henry-incinerator-seven-poetry-books-to-read-this-december/only-sing/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing.jpg" data-orig-size="652,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="only sing" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing-196x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-263444" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing-196x300.jpg" alt="" width="196" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing-196x300.jpg 196w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing-39x60.jpg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/only-sing.jpg 652w" sizes="(max-width: 196px) 100vw, 196px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>John Berryman, ed. by Shane McCrae, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9780374617943" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Only Sing</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(FSG)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Relentless, inspired &#8230; This surprise volume is a key addition to Berryman&#8217;s oeuvre.&#8221;<br />
<em>–Booklist</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263750" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/adam-morgan-john-berryman-tilar-j-mazzeo-and-more-10-new-books-out-today/screen-shot-2025-12-02-at-2-41-13-pm/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM.png" data-orig-size="950,1450" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="The Sea Captain&#8217;s Wife" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-197x300.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-671x1024.png" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-263750" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-197x300.png" alt="The Sea Captain's Wife" width="197" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-197x300.png 197w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-671x1024.png 671w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-768x1172.png 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-39x60.png 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM-33x50.png 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screen-Shot-2025-12-02-at-2.41.13-PM.png 950w" sizes="(max-width: 197px) 100vw, 197px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Tilar J. Mazzeo, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781250352583" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Sea Captain&#8217;s Wife: A True Story of Mutiny, Love, and Adventure at the Bottom of the World</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(St. Martin&#8217;s Press)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;An epic tale of courage, fortitude, and grit, brilliantly narrated in this deeply researched and compelling account.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>Siddharth Kara</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264008" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/adam-morgan-john-berryman-tilar-j-mazzeo-and-more-10-new-books-out-today/61bzyvinel-_ac_uf10001000_ql80_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg" data-orig-size="662,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Complete Notebooks, Albert Camus" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-199x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264008 aligncenter" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-199x300.jpg" alt="Complete Notebooks, Albert Camus" width="199" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-199x300.jpg 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/61BZYvInEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg 662w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 199px) 100vw, 199px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Albert Camus, trans. by Ryan Bloom, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9780226694818" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Complete Notebooks</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(University of Chicago Press)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Through some combination of his glamorous looks, his sharp mind, and his theatric early death, Camus seems always new, always pointed &#8230; Fascinating.&#8221;<br />
<em>–Open Letters Review</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263749" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/adam-morgan-john-berryman-tilar-j-mazzeo-and-more-10-new-books-out-today/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr.jpeg" data-orig-size="1400,2147" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Cape Fever, Nadia Davids" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-196x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-668x1024.jpeg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-263749" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-196x300.jpeg" alt="Cape Fever, Nadia Davids" width="196" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-196x300.jpeg 196w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-668x1024.jpeg 668w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-768x1178.jpeg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-39x60.jpeg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-1002x1536.jpeg 1002w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-1335x2048.jpeg 1335w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cape-fever-9781668090732_hr-33x50.jpeg 33w, https